(This series is entirely fictional and does not depict)

00:00:16.880 --> 00:00:20.160
(any real individuals, locations, organizations, or events.)

00:00:27.800 --> 00:00:29.320
Ladies and gentlemen,

00:00:29.360 --> 00:00:34.240
Welcome to the RoV Pro League 2026 Summer World Grand Final.

00:00:34.760 --> 00:00:38.360
And here are our two finalists.

00:00:43.000 --> 00:00:46.880
A lot of people probably wonder why we were born.

00:00:50.960 --> 00:00:53.440
Some say it's to find happiness.

00:00:56.920 --> 00:01:00.000
Others say it's to find the meaning of life.

00:01:02.520 --> 00:01:03.720
But as for me...

00:01:07.440 --> 00:01:08.880
I was born to...

00:01:09.440 --> 00:01:10.440
Win!

00:01:17.760 --> 00:01:19.320
For as long as I can remember,

00:01:19.360 --> 00:01:20.960
- I've only had one dream. - Hit it.

00:01:21.360 --> 00:01:22.040
Jump.

00:01:22.200 --> 00:01:22.720
Die.

00:01:23.560 --> 00:01:26.280
And that's to be the best gamer

00:01:26.560 --> 00:01:28.360
That no one can beat.

00:01:29.120 --> 00:01:30.240
(P'Three is the GOAT.)

00:01:30.280 --> 00:01:32.880
(No one can take him down.)

00:01:32.880 --> 00:01:34.400
(GMs, stop nerfing the heroes)

00:01:34.440 --> 00:01:35.520
(and just nerf him already.)

00:01:35.520 --> 00:01:36.640
Triple Kill!

00:01:37.120 --> 00:01:39.400
I don't care if I'm playing against pros or streamers.

00:01:39.440 --> 00:01:41.320
I don't care what game it is.

00:01:42.520 --> 00:01:44.000
And? Now what?

00:01:44.000 --> 00:01:45.400
Hey, hey. There you go.

00:01:45.400 --> 00:01:46.840
You sure that's called running?

00:01:48.640 --> 00:01:49.720
Hurry, hurry. Come on.

00:01:49.760 --> 00:01:50.760
Yeah.

00:01:52.680 --> 00:01:54.920
Sorry, kid. I'm just too good...

00:01:54.960 --> 00:01:57.160
There's only ever one outcome.

00:01:59.480 --> 00:02:01.640
GG, EZ, bro. Way too easy.

00:02:01.960 --> 00:02:06.760
And that's for me to win, win, and win again.

00:02:11.920 --> 00:02:12.640
Easy?

00:02:13.200 --> 00:02:13.840
Isn't that easy?

00:02:14.640 --> 00:02:15.680
This is too easy.

00:02:15.920 --> 00:02:17.040
Don't you think so?

00:02:17.960 --> 00:02:19.920
Tell you what, let's play this game instead.

00:02:20.240 --> 00:02:21.640
I'll carry you guys to a higher rank.

00:02:22.120 --> 00:02:23.880
I'll drop the code.

00:02:23.960 --> 00:02:26.440
Come join me, alright?

00:02:26.520 --> 00:02:28.640
If you wanna get a higher rank, come on in.

00:03:09.400 --> 00:03:11.080
- Help. - Help me, Soh.

00:03:11.120 --> 00:03:12.280
- Ow! - Soh!

00:03:13.680 --> 00:03:14.760
- Soh! - Help!

00:03:14.760 --> 00:03:16.200
- James, Arm... - Hey!

00:03:16.240 --> 00:03:17.760
- Faster, come on. - Hurry.

00:03:22.520 --> 00:03:23.240
Ouch!

00:03:31.200 --> 00:03:33.440
What are you up to, Derpy Kid?

00:03:49.480 --> 00:03:51.040
You damn bear!

00:04:15.960 --> 00:04:17.920
Let's end this game, baby.

00:04:23.200 --> 00:04:26.600
(Survivors escaped. You lost.)

00:04:29.840 --> 00:04:32.360
You goddamn bear!

00:04:37.240 --> 00:04:40.160
(Did P'Three just get wrecked? For real?)

00:04:40.200 --> 00:04:41.720
(Derya is the support player,)

00:04:41.760 --> 00:04:47.080
(but Thr33Gamer is the sufferer. LOLOLOLOL.)

00:04:47.120 --> 00:04:48.200
Derya...

00:04:51.760 --> 00:04:54.520
Derya, I'm coming for you.

00:04:55.480 --> 00:04:58.320
Derya, I'm hunting you down,

00:04:58.320 --> 00:04:59.320
You damn bear!

00:05:00.360 --> 00:05:02.600
Derya, I'm hunting you down,

00:05:02.640 --> 00:05:08.200
You damn bear!

00:05:08.720 --> 00:05:10.120
Whoa, everyone.

00:05:10.120 --> 00:05:12.480
That was one hell of a moment.

00:05:12.480 --> 00:05:13.320
He was something else.

00:05:13.320 --> 00:05:16.160
I've never seen P'Three lose his cool like that before.

00:05:16.200 --> 00:05:17.520
Now I'm dying to see

00:05:17.560 --> 00:05:19.400
What that damn bear actually looks like.

00:05:24.200 --> 00:05:25.200
Guys,

00:05:25.600 --> 00:05:26.440
I don't think...

00:05:27.440 --> 00:05:29.560
I can help myself anymore.

00:05:31.640 --> 00:05:34.680
I can't help giving this AAA game five stars.

00:05:35.400 --> 00:05:37.560
This is seriously so wholesome, guys.

00:05:37.800 --> 00:05:39.240
And I've run out of ways to praise it.

00:05:39.480 --> 00:05:42.920
I thought it'd be just a survival game,

00:05:42.920 --> 00:05:44.160
But in the end,

00:05:44.200 --> 00:05:46.480
I was in a flood of tears.

00:05:48.760 --> 00:05:51.280
The love between an ordinary person and a killer

00:05:51.480 --> 00:05:53.920
Really touched my heart, guys.

00:05:56.640 --> 00:05:58.480
Anyway, I want to thank the other five people

00:05:58.680 --> 00:06:00.160
For coming along on this journey with me.

00:06:00.560 --> 00:06:03.040
I hope we'll get to play together again in the next game.

00:06:03.640 --> 00:06:05.280
This game is seriously amazing.

00:06:07.520 --> 00:06:08.640
Soh, we've got a problem.

00:06:09.640 --> 00:06:11.200
James, Arm...

00:06:11.200 --> 00:06:12.080
- Wait, - Wait.

00:06:12.080 --> 00:06:13.640
You already know?

00:06:13.640 --> 00:06:14.720
I know.

00:06:14.760 --> 00:06:15.720
- That? - That?

00:06:15.880 --> 00:06:18.040
After waiting five years for this game,

00:06:18.080 --> 00:06:19.960
The killer ends up killing the main character

00:06:20.000 --> 00:06:21.720
Even though they're still in love.

00:06:21.760 --> 00:06:22.480
Jeez!

00:06:22.520 --> 00:06:23.640
That's not it, man.

00:06:25.160 --> 00:06:27.000
The one who's about to die isn't the guy in the game.

00:06:27.200 --> 00:06:28.280
It's you.

00:06:29.760 --> 00:06:30.800
Am I going to die?

00:06:33.640 --> 00:06:35.360
How is that even possible?

00:06:35.840 --> 00:06:38.160
Derya, I'm hunting you down,

00:06:38.200 --> 00:06:43.800
You damn bear.

00:06:47.960 --> 00:06:50.400
The killer you juked last night...

00:06:50.440 --> 00:06:51.880
Was Thr33Gamer.

00:06:54.320 --> 00:06:56.840
(Found you, you damn bear. @Thr33Gamer)

00:06:57.480 --> 00:07:01.320
(P'Three has been looking for you since yesterday. @Thr33Gamer)

00:07:01.360 --> 00:07:04.400
(Time for a rematch, bro. @Thr33Gamer)

00:07:04.800 --> 00:07:08.040
(Let's share this so P'Three sees it. @Thr33Gamer)

00:07:08.760 --> 00:07:10.720
Sh*t, look at that.

00:07:11.320 --> 00:07:12.280
The viewer count...

00:07:12.720 --> 00:07:13.760
- Five thousand... - Five thousand...

00:07:13.960 --> 00:07:15.520
Sh*t, where the hell did they all come from?

00:07:19.840 --> 00:07:22.480
(Add me right now before I come hunting for you.)

00:07:22.720 --> 00:07:24.280
- Holy sh*t. - Holy sh*t.

00:07:27.160 --> 00:07:27.960
P'Three!

00:07:31.840 --> 00:07:32.640
Hold on.

00:07:32.800 --> 00:07:34.880
You're about to strike it rich, man.

00:07:35.000 --> 00:07:35.920
Look at all these donations.

00:07:38.880 --> 00:07:40.120
Having you guys here

00:07:40.800 --> 00:07:42.400
Is worth more than a billion dollars to me.

00:07:51.520 --> 00:07:52.280
Hold up.

00:07:52.480 --> 00:07:53.640
Are you acting weird, too?

00:07:53.960 --> 00:07:54.920
I have other reasons.

00:07:55.520 --> 00:07:56.360
Like what?

00:07:57.320 --> 00:07:59.280
I think P'Three is acting a bit weird.

00:08:00.320 --> 00:08:01.600
He's so desperate to beat you

00:08:01.600 --> 00:08:03.000
